These are Puzzles for 7x2 Level 1

.:: Puzzle 7x2-Level-1-1::.
There are 2 different favourite beverages: tea, lemonade
The people have 2 different hobbies: filmmaking, camping
The people have 2 different jobs:  librarian, software-developer
The people perfer 2 different movie-genres: animation, time-travel
There are 2 different nationalities: spanish, dutch
2 different pets are kept: horse, bird
The people use 2 different means of transport: van, skateboard
1. the person drinking tea is on the far right##1
2. the software-developer is on the far right##1
3. the person driving the skateboard is on the left of the person who's hobby is camping##1
4. the owner of the horse is the dutch##1
5. the person watching time-travel movies is on the far left##1
6. the owner of the bird is on the right of the person driving the skateboard##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |     2      |
| Beverage      | lemonade     | tea       |
| Hobby         | filmmaking   | camping     |
| Job           | librarian | software-developer   |
| Movie-Genre   | time-travel   | animation  |
| Nationality   | dutch | spanish |
| Pet           | horse      | bird     |
| Transport     | skateboard    | van   |

