.:: Puzzle 7x2-Level-1-2::.
There are 2 different favourite beverages: water, tea
The people have 2 different hobbies: camping, chess
The people have 2 different jobs:  engineer, social-worker
The people prefer 2 different music-genres: punk, d&b
There are 2 different nationalities: british, spanish
2 different pets are kept: rat, bird
The people use 2 different means of transport: helicopter, ship
1. the social-worker is on the right of the person who's hobby is chess##1
2. the owner of the bird is the person driving the ship##1
3. the person driving the helicopter is on the left of the fan of punk##1
4. the spanish is on the far right##1
5. the person drinking water is the owner of the rat##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |       1        |    2     |
| Beverage      | water    | tea |
| Hobby         | chess        | camping  |
| Job           | engineer | social-worker  |
| Music-Genre   | d&b            | punk    |
| Nationality   | british     | spanish   |
| Pet           | rat         | bird    |
| Transport     | helicopter           | ship      |

